    Black Aracnia leads the way down the hall. Behinde her Paralysis, 
Quickstrike, and Darkmouse follow. She was headed for the bridge to take over 
once and for all.
    The doors slide open and Black Aracnia enters. Paralysis signals to the 
others to stay put until Aracnia said what she needed to say. "Wait here. 
Aracnia is gonna tell him off."
    Aracnia stands before Rampage. "Now, Rampage. I have control of this 
ship, and several armed associates that will fight along with me. Let me rule 
the Predacons with Megatron now, peacefully, or refuse and die. I hate to be 
so blunt...but were short on time."
